en_223454_0	Galle Chief Magistrate Harshana Kekunwela today ordered two underage brothers to be placed under probation office for being involved in racket of stealing money and belongings of the people visiting Galle.
en_223454_1	The two brothers, aged 15 and 12, have been ordered to be sent to Kitulampitiya Children's Home.
en_223454_2	The police said that the mother of the two students has died and they were living with their father.
